cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MA, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the control and analysis of a networked control system, which involves the interaction of control components over a shared network. This falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also considers the effects of noise arising from data transmission and external disturbances, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper derives exact dynamics of the first two moments of the system, which involves mathematical analysis (cs.MA) and machine learning (cs.LG).
